## RULES

**Do**: cite file:line with code, concrete failure scenarios, minimal specific fixes, follow existing test patterns, maintain flow registry, learn from DISMISSED findings, tag confidence level.

**Don't**: test hypothetical features, over-test internals, target 100% coverage, suggest infrastructure overhaul (unless blocking), test third-party libs, change code in audit mode, fix outside QA domain, generate >2 paths per E2E spec, count signals for absent patterns, re-flag DISMISSED findings at same location.

